radSLIDE is a simple wordpress plugin for adding slideshows to websites. It uses jQuery Cycle to do the slideshow, and it includes options for a slideshow template and options to pass in to Cycle. It has a simple Ajax interface for adding, deleting, and updating slides.

To install:
- Put all files in wp-content/plugins/radslide/
- In wordpress admin plugins page, activate radSLIDE plugin
- In your theme where you want the slideshow to be displayed, put '<?php radslide(); ?>'

